T1  - The Escalation Phenomenon Reconsidered: Decision Dilemmas or Decision Errors?
AU  - Bowen, Michael G.
Y1  - 1987/01/01
PY  - 1987
DA  - 1987/01/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.1987.4306470
