N2  - The article discusses the author's experiences and current news relating to the editing of the journal ?Academy of Management Review.? The author states that the percentage of manuscripts that have been accepted so far is lower than the target of 14%, and describes the nature of manuscripts that have been submitted. The author chronicles resignations from the board and announces new additions, including Rabi S. Bhagat of the University of Texas, Dallas; John D. Hatfield of the University of Georgia; and William Starbuck of New York University.
